research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Palmer, Texas, operates with a Mayor and five Council Members, all elected at-large. Information was gathered from the official City of Palmer website and the Texas State Directory Online. There were some discrepancies across different search results regarding the full list of council members, but the provided list represents the most consistent and current information found. The Texas Municipal League directory, while comprehensive, appeared to have a 2019 copyright, suggesting it might not be the most up-to-date source for all positions.
